Dear Sir,

We work with Venture Capitalist, Angel Investors, Personal Investors and
Peer to Peer Lenders whose investment fund were pooled together through
Hedge Fund Service for Project and Business finance purposes.

If you have any viable project that requires funding, we are ready and
willing to work on the project if it is technically sound, financially
rewarding, economically feasible and commercially viable.

Our office is open 9:00 am to 6:00 pm six days a week. We look forward to
working with you.


Thank you.

William James
International Financial Advisor
Financial Freedom Sagl
via Lucino 3,
6932 Breganzona,
Switzerland.
